      <title>经济学家洪磊：中国需要采取更多措施提振房地产信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-02/china-needs-to-do-more-to-boost-confidence-in-property-economist-hong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[GROW Investment Group 合伙人兼首席经济学家洪灏讨论了中国经济状况以及政府支持增长的努力。中国剩余的增长引擎正出现疲软迹象，而房地产市场继续拖累经济。洪灏在“彭博：中国秀”上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-02/china-needs-to-do-more-to-boost-confidence-in-property-economist-hong</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 01:46:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
