      <title>分析师称日经指数可能增持良品计划，并削减日本制纸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/nikkei-may-add-ryohin-keikaku-cut-nippon-paper-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本日经 225 股票平均指数编制者预计将最早于周一公布其定期评估结果，分析师预测该蓝筹指数将加入无印良品连锁运营商良品计划株式会社，并删除日本制纸工业株式会社。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/nikkei-may-add-ryohin-keikaku-cut-nippon-paper-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:46:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国 8 月份制造业和房地产数据恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-02/china-s-factory-and-housing-data-worsen-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月份，中国工厂活动连续第四个月萎缩，而 100 家最大房地产公司的新屋销售额较上年同期下降约 26.8%。彭博电视台的 Minmin Low 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-02/china-s-factory-and-housing-data-worsen-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国大宗商品库存激增反映经济困境之深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/china-s-bulging-commodity-stockpiles-lay-depth-of-slowdown-bare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国主要原材料库存不断增加，表明经济活动仍然过于疲软，无法消化造成钢铁、大豆等产品价格暴跌的过剩产能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/china-s-bulging-commodity-stockpiles-lay-depth-of-slowdown-bare</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 00:01:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
